<p>{{{{translate this id="greeting"}}}}Hi {{customer.firstName}},{{{{/translate}}}}</p>
<p>{{{{translate this id="intro"}}}}Great news — your order has been shipped.{{{{/translate}}}}</p>
<p>{{{{translate this id="tracking.info"}}}}Your package is being delivered by {{carrier}}. Your tracking code is {{trackingCode}}.{{{{/translate}}}}</p>
<p><a href="{{trackingUrl}}">{{{{translate this id="tracking.cta"}}}}Track your package{{{{/translate}}}}</a></p>
<p>{{{{translate this id="delivery.estimate"}}}}Estimated delivery: {{estimatedDelivery}}{{{{/translate}}}}</p>
<hr>
<p><small>{{{{translate this id="support.html"}}}}Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.{{{{/translate}}}}</small></p>
<p><small>{{{{translate this id="legal"}}}}You received this email because you have an account with us.{{{{/translate}}}}</small></p>
